[ ] X402 SIGNATURE VALIDATION
    MANUAL / BLOCKED BY PROTOCOL SIGNING REQUIREMENT.
    The payment proof signature field is now required and structurally
    validated, but it is not cryptographically verified yet. On-chain transfer
    scan remains the live guard. Missing requirement: canonical proof signing
    payload and exact Ed25519/Secp256k1 signature encoding from the
    wallet/facilitator flow.
    File: api/casper/x402.py → X402Verifier.verify()

[x] X402 NONCE PERSISTENCE
    DONE. Consumed nonces are persisted to Supabase table x402_used_nonces.
    Duplicate insert failures reject reused nonces. Migration 003 adds the
    nonce table and TTL index.
    Files: api/casper/x402.py, api/db/supabase.py,
           api/db/migrations/003_x402_nonces_and_getter_cache.sql

